(Those without) will call out "were we not with you?" (The
			others) will reply "True! but ye led yourselves into temptation;
			ye looked forward (to our ruin); ye doubted (Allah's promise);
			and (your false) desires deceived you; until there issued the
			Command of Allah.  And the Deceiver deceived you in respect of
			Allah. <span class='fn'>5292</span> <span class='fn'>5293</span>
